cdata.name: Russiacoin
cdata.desc: Russiacoin is a Scrypt PoW/PoScryptocurrency made for all peoplearoundthe world and escpecially the russian altcoin-community. Russiacoin will be thefirst coin to use the GDR (=golden readjustment algorithm) which is just similar to std.diff. adj. but has a adapted PoS start diff. so it will be a hybrid PoW/PoS in the PoW stage to allow an stabilization of PoS diff. within the PoW stage to make sure the network runsfluid.
